nodes.title: Guidence Type Explanation
widgets_values:
Only Use 1 and 2 as option
1 is using prompt as guidance useful for direct guidance
For example, text editing on small area

2 is using Redux as guidance which is default
It is suggested to use redux guidance until it doesn't work

nodes.title: General Parameter Explanation
widgets_values:
Seed: Control generation

Output Size: Control generation long edge width

Buffer: Control context window size
Larger context window could lead to better fuse result
Smaller context window could more focuse on that area
Usually large buffer is better than small buffer

Mask Expand: Initial Mask expand value
Mask Blur = Mask Expand / 2

Denoise: Denoising strength.
Default is 1 which is fullly denoise the masked area
You could use lower value for patial denoise.
It is useful for fixing task. For example: fixing hand

nodes.title: Final Mask Type Explanation
widgets_values:
Control auto masking expand value

Mask Blur = Mask Expand / 2

Larger value could fix edge vestige
